[gd_scene load_steps=120 format=3]

; LAVA — Volcanic domain of magma, ruins, and dark crystals.
; =====================================================================
; Spawn: (0, 1, 35) on the outer basalt approach ledge, volcano ahead.
;
; LANDMARKS (clockwise from spawn):
;   - Entry approach ledge + dock of cracked basalt
;   - Stepping-stone archipelago (15+ platforms over lava sea)
;   - CENTRAL VOLCANO (hero piece, ~25m tall cone):
;       * Spiral external ramp, ~8 short prism segments carved around
;       * Crater at summit with CSG-subtracted sphere + lava pool
;       * Interior chamber (CSG carved) reached by crater descent
;         or by side cave at base
;         - Lava river across floor (y=-1 thin plane)
;         - 2 stone bridges arching over the river
;         - Lava tube tunnels branching off (N and E)
;         - Central dais holds the Core Star
;   - Obsidian crystal cave (far NE platform) — basalt outcrop,
;     CSG-hollowed, plain_black crystal prisms + ember glow-cracks,
;     hidden 1up
;   - Fire-plant forest (island W) — piranha hazard gauntlet
;   - Ancient forge ruins (far E platform) — anvil, bellows, furnace
;     with CSG-cut opening + ember glow inside; cauldron, tongs;
;     coins hidden in furnace; cap_metal inside bellows
;   - Rock arch bridges (x3) — CSG-subtracted tunnels through basalt
;   - Fire fall + secret tunnel behind the cascade
;   - Magma chamber lookout (high platform w/ telescope + bench)
;   - Dragon skeleton (far SW platform) — serpentine fossil
;
; CSG usage (SUBTRACTION = operation 2) concentrated in:
;   VolcanoInteriorCarver (sphere + cylinders carving chamber out
;     of stacked basalt blocks), CraterCarver (top sphere), ArchCarvers
;     (rotated cylinders through basalt boxes), ObsidianCaveCarver
;     (interior void), ForgeFurnaceCarver (door + firebox),
;     CrackRockCarvers (small ember-lit splits), FireFallTunnelCarver.
;
; CONTENT: 8 bobombs, 5 flame-plants, 3 goombas, 2 chuckyas,
;   3 cuttlefish ("thermals"), 1 bobomb buddy (forge keeper);
;   45 yellow, 8 red coins, 3 stars (summit, core, cave), 4 oneups,
;   1 cap_metal.

